fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.forward_chaining

Class SccChase<T extends AtomSet>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.api.forward_chaining.AbstractChase<Rule,T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Chase, Profilable

    public class SccChase<T extends AtomSet>
extends AbstractChase<Rule,T>
    This Chase apply rules following the layers of the Strongly Connected Components Graph (SCCG) of the Graph Of Rule Dependencies (GRD). It applies rules layer by layer, indeed a rule from a layer of the SCCG can not trigger a rule from a previous layer.
    This chase is not breadth first.
